snippet.title: Bundy Ranch Conspiracy Debunked

localized.description:
Are Harry Reid and a Chinese company (building a solar plant) behind the already infamous standoff between Cliven Bundy and the Feds? Is Bundy right about his cattle being able to graze on federal land without having to pay taxes? The Young Turks host Cenk Uygur breaks it down.

Read more about the Reid conspiracy here: http://www.snopes.com/politics/conspiracy/nevada.asp

Read more about the federal land issue here: http://thehill.com/blogs/e2-wire/e2-wire/203525-feds-play-waiting-game-after-nevada-ranch-standoff-ends

Young Turk (n), 1. Young progressive or insurgent member of an institution, movement, or political party. 2. Young person who rebels against authority or societal expectations. (American Heritage Dictionary)
